6.20	Casper's_Haunted_Christmas	Casper's Haunted Christmas	Casper's Haunted Christmas is a 2000 direct-to-video film produced by Harvey Comics and Mainframe Entertainment and released by Universal Pictures on October 31, 2000. Unlike its direct-to-video predecessors, this video was completely computer animated. It stars Brendan Ryan Barrett as the voice of Casper the Friendly Ghost. Randy Travis provided original music.	
